{"tid":1562770,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"留意到有藍屍, 將《願榮光歸香港》拎黎用","createTime":"2019-09-12T06:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:06:35.000Z","uid":227801,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"248e03c4aabff0f6c65766e3adcd81724ab32ecd","tid":1562770,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:52:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XIICKLB9zKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXIICKLB9zKE&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=aea3c5f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XIICKLB9zKE</a><br />\n偷創作者心血黎用當然係仆街陷家剷<br />\n<br />\n但係留意返，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>通常國歌先可以俾同政見嘅人都用都唱</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你有冇見過其他一般社運歌可以？<br />\n<br />\n唔該藍屍們留意返有冇endorse左首歌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有共鳴不妨一齊出嚟唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意返入面有光復香港，時代革命架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61acaf419aef7e951666877a3ae09a5350c32f2","tid":1562770,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:52:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%